e citizen burdens. Previously, many cases went to the state secretariat, causing delays. The amendment provides a clear legal framework for these regularizations.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/maharashtra-land-regularisation-powers-decentralised-local-authorities-to-manage-90-cases/129815393?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-40180/129815393.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}]}